Al Fayed’s Paris Ritz to Close for 27 Months, Metro Reports

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-10-18T11:03:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/al-fayed-s-paris-ritz-to-close-for-27-months-metro-reports.html
The Paris Ritz, owned by Mohamed Al
Fayed, will close for 27 months from next year for renovation,
the Metro free newspaper reported on its website, citing hotel
management.  The work will mean that 450 of the hotel’s 500 employees
will lose their jobs, according to Metro.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  